references:
There are nearly 400 features in the ranking model of our company’s E-commerce Recommender System. We analyzed the importance of all these features for both click-through rate (CTR) and conversion rate (CVR) tasks in our multi-task learning (MTL) ranking model using Permutation Feature Importance.
